This is the Worlds first Lunar lake powered mini PC! The ASUS NUC 14 Pro Ai is here and it’s powered by the Intel Core Ultra 9 288V with 32GB of LPDDR5X ram running at 8533MHZ! Along with this we also get the Intel ARC 240V iGPU with a clock speed of 2050MHZ making it the fastest Lunar lake iGPU yet! An all new tool less chassis design allows anyone to easily upgrade the storage. We do an unboxing run some Ai work loads, test some benchmarks and see how it handles AAA gaming! #asus #minipc #minipc
